German and Dutch

                            apertium-de-nl
===============================================================================

This is an Apertium language pair for translating between German and 
Dutch. What you can use this language package for:

* Translating between German and Dutch
* Morphological analysis of German and Dutch
* Part-of-speech tagging of German and Dutch

For information on the latter two points, see subheading "For more 
information" below

Requirements
===============================================================================

You will need the following software installed:

* lttoolbox (>= 3.1.2)
* apertium (>= 3.1.1)

If this does not make any sense, we recommend you look at: www.apertium.org

Compiling
===============================================================================

Given the requirements being installed, you should be able to just run:

$ ./configure 
$ make
# make install

You can use ./autogen.sh instead of ./configure you're compiling from
SVN. If you're using a --prefix to ./configure, make sure it's the
same one you used to install apertium itself.

Testing
===============================================================================

If you are in the source directory after running make, the following
commands should work:

$ echo "Mein Luftkissenfahrzeug ist voller Aale" | apertium -d . de-nl
*Mein *Luftkissenfahrzeug @sein @voll @Aal~

$ echo "Mijn luchtkussenboot zit vol paling" | apertium -d . nl-de
*Mijn *luchtkussenboot *zit *vol *paling

After installing somewhere in $PATH, you should be able to do e.g.

$ echo "Mein Luftkissenfahrzeug ist voller Aale" | apertium de-nl
*Mein *Luftkissenfahrzeug @sein @voll @Aal~

There are no regression tests yet.

Files and data
===============================================================================

* apertium-de-nl.de.dix        - Monolingual dictionary for German
* apertium-de-nl.de-nl.dix     - Bilingual dictionary 
* apertium-de-nl.nl.dix        - Monolingual dictionary for Dutch
* apertium-de-nl.de-nl.t1x     - Transfer rules for translating into Dutch
* apertium-de-nl.nl-de.t1x     - Transfer rules for translating into German
* de-nl.prob                   - Tagger model for German
* nl-de.prob                   - Tagger model for Dutch
* apertium-de-nl.de.tsx        - Tagger training rules for German
* modes.xml                    - Translation modes

For more information
===============================================================================

* http://wiki.apertium.org/wiki/Installation
* http://wiki.apertium.org/wiki/apertium-de-nl
* http://wiki.apertium.org/wiki/Using_an_lttoolbox_dictionary

